No big deal.

599
00:52:57,360 --> 00:53:00,680
What was she doing there?
- I look after her sometimes.

600
00:53:01,720 --> 00:53:04,680
You look after a kid?
- Yeah. - Pinch me!

601
00:53:05,800 --> 00:53:08,080
