675
00:59:35,800 --> 00:59:37,400
Do you get it now?

676
00:59:39,640 --> 00:59:40,600
I don't know,

677
00:59:42,600 --> 00:59:43,800
but I think so.

678
00:59:54,600 --> 00:59:55,800
How do I look?

679
00:59:56,880 --> 00:59:58,200
Good. Where are you going?

680
00:59:59,120 --> 01:00:02,840
